      <title>科罗拉多州共和党人博伯特将于 2024 年切换选区参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/colorado-republican-boebert-switching-districts-to-run-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自科罗拉多州的直言不讳的保守派共和党众议员劳伦·博伯特表示，她明年将竞选连任——但在不同的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/colorado-republican-boebert-switching-districts-to-run-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 03:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
